FBIS3-48346 "dreas016_c_94010" FBIS-EAS-94-016 Document Type:Daily Report 25 Jan 1994 North Korea Family Receives Kim Il-song Letter SK2201110094 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1036 GMT 22 Jan 94 SK2201110094 Pyongyang KCNA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Pyongyang, January 22 (KCNA) -- The message of condolence sent by the great leader President Kim Il-song upon the death of Rev. Mun Ik-hwan was conveyed to the bereaved family of the deceased. His message was conveyed to the bereaved family through the funeral committee for Rev. Mun Ik-hwan.
